.gsd/REQUIREMENTS.md:51:### R008 — The platform includes an extensible model/provider configuration skeleton and M001 chat prefers a real configured LLM provider/API when credentials are available, with mock responses only as fallback for smoke tests, CI, or local development without credentials.
